14.Sum of squares of first n natural numbers
n=10
total=0
if n>0:
  for i in range(1,n+1):
    total=total+(i**2) 
  print(f'Sum of squares of first {n} natural numbers:',total)
===========
15.Cube sum of first n natural numbers
n=10
total=0
if n>0:
  for i in range(1,n+1):
    total=total+(i**3) 
  print(f'Sum of cube of first {n} natural numbers:',total)
